author: Fextralife
description:
Elden Ring Nightreign Duchess Build - Divine Duchess (Non-Status Effect Build)
In this Elden Ring Nightreign video, I'm going to be showing my nonmeta Duchess build. This is a build that doesn't focus on poison or frostbite. Neither of those are in the build. The reason I created it is a lot of people need a build with Duchess that will take on the last boss, which is immune to both of those status effects, and I wanted to showcase a build that you can play even against other bosses that work really well.

Elden Ring Nightreign Wiki: https://eldenringnightreign.wiki.fextralife.com/Elden+Ring+Nightreign+Wiki
